<plot>In this entry from the "Memories from Melody Lane" series, clips from four movie musicals are shown, each featuring a single song. After each song, narrator 'Art Gilmore' (qv) invites the audience to sing along with the Melody Makers, as cards with the song's lyrics are displayed on the screen. For the complete list of songs and performers, check the Soundtrack listing.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?333599</url></doc>
